Class InteractiveClient.InteractiveLexer

  • java.lang.Object
    • antlr.CharScanner
      • edu.caltech.nanodb.sqlparse.NanoSqlLexer
        • edu.caltech.nanodb.client.InteractiveClient.InteractiveLexer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    antlr.TokenStream, NanoSqlParserTokenTypes
    Enclosing class:
    InteractiveClient

    protected static class InteractiveClient.InteractiveLexer
extends NanoSqlLexer
    This class provides a simple wrapper around the NanoSQL Lexer so that the program can present a more user-friendly prompt for multi-line command input.
